_:Nb6d25df3efc04789b5bda762586d7f1b <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Daniel Flury was appointed Operations Director for HMCTS in March 2024, leading nearly 15,000 people working across courts, tribunals and national services.</p>\n\n<p>Daniel joined the civil service in 1999 and has held a number of operational and policy positions within HMCTS, the Legal Aid Agency and the Ministry of Justice.</p>\n\n<p>As well as a HMCTS Cluster Manager, Transformation Director and Delivery Director, Daniel has also been the Programme Director of three Major Government programmes (including the HMCTS Crime Programme) and is a graduate of the Major Projects Leadership Academy. He has also been the Service Owner for Tribunals and for Crime and the Access to Justice Policy Director in MoJ.</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
